            "text": "The ruling, which will now stand, invalidated a key federal permit for the pipeline on the grounds that it violated the National Environmental Policy Act. The court required the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers to conduct a comprehensive environmental review of the pipeline’s route underneath Lake Oahe, on the border of North and South Dakota, which Indigenous communities ",
