            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " sent a letter to Starbucks’ CEO on Wednesday in support of the Starbucks Workers United union, urging the company to “follow the letter and spirit of the law by allowing your employees free choice in joining a union.”",
